p.me:
\begin{array}{rcl} \displaystyle \int_0^{5} (4 e^x+5 \sin x)\, dx \amp =\amp   
\displaystyle  4 e^x-5 \cos x  \Big]_0^{5}
\\ \amp =\amp  (4 e^{5} - 5 \cos 5) - (4 e^0 - 5 \cos0 ) 
\\ \amp =\amp  4 e^{5} - 5 \cos 5  + 1 
\end{array}

