statement.p:
\begin{aligned}
2x+1 \amp= 3
\end{aligned}
Now subtract 1 from each side.
\begin{aligned}
2x   \amp= 2
\end{aligned}
Now divide by 2 on each side.
\begin{aligned}
x    \amp= 1
\end{aligned}

We should also test when the <md> is within a list.




Start a list.






